author: HBO Max
description:
Join James Gunn with co-hosts Steve Agee (John Economos) and Jennifer Holland (Emilia Harcourt) with special guest Joel Kinnaman (Rick Flag Jr.) for the latest episode of Peacemaker: The Official Podcast. The team explores Season 2, Episode 3, "Another Rick Up My Sleeve" where Joel discusses reprising his role as Rick Flag Jr. and shares stories from both Peacemaker and The Suicide Squad. The crew dives into the episode’s multiverse twist, character dynamics, and the emotional connections between Harcourt and Rick Flag Jr. Listener questions, set stories, and a preview of what’s to come round out this lively and insightful episode.
